      <title>中国假日消费回暖 市场担忧经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/china-holiday-spending-gain-a-blip-for-markets-worried-by-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，中国重要节假日期间消费较疫情前水平小幅上升，但这一反弹并未影响仍关注中国经济困境加剧程度的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/china-holiday-spending-gain-a-blip-for-markets-worried-by-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 09:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
