    <item>
      <title>印度考虑放宽大米出口限制，帮助全球供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/india-considers-relaxing-export-curbs-on-non-basmati-rice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度正考虑放宽对非巴斯马蒂大米海外销售的限制，几天前，印度刚刚取消了优质大米出口底价，此举有望增加全球大米供应，为数十亿人口提供粮食。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/india-considers-relaxing-export-curbs-on-non-basmati-rice</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 07:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者关注中国风险，达利欧淡化美联储下一步举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/dalio-downplays-fed-s-next-move-as-investors-warn-of-china-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个区域论坛的与会者表示，美联储本周降息幅度不会对全球投资者产生重大影响，不过中国经济放缓带来的风险仍困扰着他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/dalio-downplays-fed-s-next-move-as-investors-warn-of-china-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:28:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
